109
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:21,690
That's called self-destruction.

110
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:44,480
Mrs. Song.

111
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,940
It's Diandian, right?

112
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:55,000
Everything's fine with him now.

113
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:57,720
What happened?

114
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,450
Being together isn't easy,

115
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:06,680
