116
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,280
okay?

117
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,800
Diandian,

118
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,320
this is Mrs. Song.

119
00:11:18,160 --> 00:11:19,090
Nice to meet you.

120
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,880
Did some people just

121
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:22,600
mistake you for my son?

122
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,320
Yes.

123
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:29,200
He's only been here three times

124
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,680
and never danced with me once.

125
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:40,940
Please sit.

126
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,380
I have something to announce:

127
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:52,760
Mrs. Song and I are officially together now.

128
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:55,480
All right.

129
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,760
We're in public,

130
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:01,620
why are you getting so emotional?

131
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,700
Congratulations.

132
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:03,930
Is that sincere?

133
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:09,280
Well, you're all having a good time anyway.

134
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:13,800
Do you know how many years I've supported your career?

135
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:16,080
Song Guanwang is now my partner,

136
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:17,760
and also your boss.

137
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,080
You should sincerely

138
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:23,080
congratulate us.

139
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,890
How should I congratulate you?

140
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,640
Dance.

141
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:31,420
Come on, dance!

142
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,360
Thank you.

143
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:44,760
I'll come dance with you more often.

144
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,650
You're not going back to Hangzhou?

145
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:51,720
No, I'm not.

146
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,640
I'm staying in Beijing with her.

147
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:05,800
Didn't she say she forgot all about you?

148
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,340
She remembers you now?

149
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:11,880
No.

150
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:16,920
Just look at her eyes.

151
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,770
How could she possibly forget you?

152
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:22,800
Look at how head over heels she is.

153
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,400
Actually,

154
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:32,160
