155
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,020
Not forgetting

156
00:13:33,680 --> 00:13:34,840
is the problem.

157
00:13:38,280 --> 00:13:40,340
She called me Auntie Song right away.

158
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,520
She remembers me,

159
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:45,210
so how could she forget you?

160
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:55,570
She called you Auntie Song.

161
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:02,320
Where are you going?

162
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,120
Uncle Qiao,

163
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:10,840
