164
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:15,460
Everything good between you two now?

165
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:17,960
Yes, it's fine.

166
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:18,840
I stayed

167
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:21,560
at her place last night.

168
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,120
Well done.

169
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:29,400
Uncle Qiao, did you need something from me?

170
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:31,080
Did you dance?

171
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:32,400
Yes, I did.

172
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,250
Then that's all.

173
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:36,760
I'll be going then.

174
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:41,050
Goodbye, Mrs. Song.

175
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:46,720
Dance.

176
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:12,240
Louder.

177
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:12,920
Good,

178
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:26,240
good.

179
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:47,700
I said I'd sponsor you with a set of speakers,

180
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:49,640
remember?

181
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:50,200
Yeah,

182
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:53,920
