185
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:02,040
Look at that dancing.

186
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:15,680
Why did you leave?

187
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:19,540
I wanted to go home.

188
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:21,500
There's so much stuff.

189
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:25,440
That was a relative's mother just now,

190
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,200
Mrs. Song.

191
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:34,200
I wanted to introduce you to her,

192
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:36,440
since we'll be in Beijing often

193
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:38,440
and you'll meet eventually.

194
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:40,640
Okay.

195
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,900
Did you call her Mrs. Song?

196
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:44,880
No,

197
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:48,220
it's the first time meeting her and I don't know her.

198
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,450
I'll do it next time.

199
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:55,780
The car's here.

200
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:56,840
Let's get in.

201
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:28,560
Just now when we met,

202
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:31,500
