203
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:34,640
Who said that?

204
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:37,840
Mrs. Song.

205
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:47,120
I was actually wondering

206
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:49,120
