207
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:54,280
We've already been introduced now.

208
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,280
Diandian.

209
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,960
Did you remember?

210
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:05,570
Or did you never forget?

211
00:18:16,080 --> 00:18:17,540
