212
00:18:21,800 --> 00:18:23,130
I want to hear you say it.

213
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:31,360
I just want to say

214
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,280
meeting you

215
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:34,480
is really fortunate.

216
00:18:37,280 --> 00:18:38,360
Unfortunately,

217
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:42,400
I didn't meet you sooner.

218
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:44,600
Fortunately,

219
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:46,960
meeting earlier

220
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:49,220
