221
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:52,360
Unfortunately,

222
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,600
we've already met before.

223
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:57,760
Fortunately,

224
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:58,920
