228
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:19,920
Fortunately,

229
00:19:21,720 --> 00:19:23,650
this fortunate-unfortunate game

230
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:26,480
we also played in Hangzhou.

231
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:30,760
Really?

232
00:19:35,240 --> 00:19:36,040
I thought

233
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:39,700
I fell in love with a new Shi Diandian.

234
00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:43,620
You had another Diandian before?

235
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:49,000
