239
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:24,760
Sorry, master.

240
00:20:36,840 --> 00:20:37,640
Diandian.

241
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:42,760
Diandian.

242
00:21:17,360 --> 00:21:19,760
You haven't forgotten anything, have you?

243
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:21,300
Did you come to Beijing

244
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:23,480
