245
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:27,210
Isn't this good enough now?

246
00:21:27,920 --> 00:21:29,250
The past doesn't count.

247
00:21:32,760 --> 00:21:33,360
But you're

248
00:21:34,720 --> 00:21:36,780
still the same Diandian from before.

249
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:42,440
