255
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,760
Let's go home.

256
00:22:16,800 --> 00:22:18,130
I'm heading back first.

257
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:05,880
Mom.

258
00:25:06,080 --> 00:25:07,120
What day is today?

259
00:25:08,040 --> 00:25:09,240
The worst day ever.

260
00:25:09,960 --> 00:25:10,760
Why?

261
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:14,640
