262
00:25:15,560 --> 00:25:16,360
Where is he?

263
00:25:17,320 --> 00:25:18,650
He hasn't come back yet.

264
00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:19,780
What happened?

265
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:23,930
The day Xu Tian came to Beijing,

266
00:25:24,760 --> 00:25:26,280
I decided to forget him,

267
00:25:27,440 --> 00:25:30,100
but when I woke up, I hadn't forgotten anything.

268
00:25:31,360 --> 00:25:33,020
I'm afraid he won't come back,

269
00:25:33,040 --> 00:25:35,560
and I don't have the courage to find him in Beijing.

270
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:37,000
I hate myself so much.

271
00:25:37,800 --> 00:25:38,960
After thinking about it, I just...

272
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:40,160
Don't think about it.

273
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:41,370
Tell that to Xu Tian.

274
00:25:41,600 --> 00:25:42,560
Tell him what?

275
00:25:43,040 --> 00:25:45,240
He likes who I've been these three days,

276
00:25:46,080 --> 00:25:47,080
and just like him,

277
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:49,480
