285
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:05,730
Who bought them?

286
00:26:05,800 --> 00:26:06,930
Did Xu Tian buy them?

287
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,600
I bought them myself.

288
00:26:10,200 --> 00:26:12,330
These three days have been wonderful,

289
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:15,400
all the bad things from before are gone.

290
00:26:20,720 --> 00:26:22,320
But there's nothing I can do,

291
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:24,520
the bad things

292
00:26:24,760 --> 00:26:27,420
will always disappear along with the good ones.

293
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:29,420
I'm hanging up.

294
00:26:59,400 --> 00:27:00,200
You're back.

295
00:27:01,120 --> 00:27:03,000
I just went to buy something else.

296
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:05,610
Let me take that.

297
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:16,600
The food's gone cold.

298
00:27:17,120 --> 00:27:18,280
There's hot food in the processor,

299
00:27:18,280 --> 00:27:19,140
help yourself.

300
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:21,760
I'll go put the sheets and covers on.

301
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:09,600
I'm late today

302
00:28:11,280 --> 00:28:13,010
because I went to buy you a cake.

303
00:28:13,120 --> 00:28:14,580
It's your birthday today.

304
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:33,610
The pillowcases aren't on yet.

305
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:35,890
We can do that later,

306
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,640
make a wish first.

307
00:29:09,880 --> 00:29:12,540
I'll turn on the lights after you make your wish.

308
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:14,080
And then?

309
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:16,760
We'll eat cake

310
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:18,280
and chat a bit.

311
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:27,600
No one else should hear when you make a wish.

312
00:29:29,080 --> 00:29:29,810
Then should I

313
00:29:30,920 --> 00:29:31,720
cover

314
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:34,080
my ears?

315
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:35,320
No.

316
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:52,400
I'm grateful to have met you in this lifetime.

317
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:53,520
I am Xu Tian.

318
00:29:53,760 --> 00:29:54,360
I know.

319
00:29:54,360 --> 00:29:56,600
I make qipaos.

320
00:29:58,080 --> 00:29:58,880
Give me.

321
00:30:01,360 --> 00:30:03,960
Let me know what love is.

322
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:07,400
My mother passed away when I was little,

323
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:10,120
and I became obsessive and insecure,

324
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:12,360
distrusting everything.

325
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:16,600
Actually, I just didn't trust myself.

326
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:20,160
Thankfully, I have you,

327
00:30:20,760 --> 00:30:22,400
who makes me feel hope,

328
00:30:23,360 --> 00:30:24,480
and feel loved.

329
00:30:55,640 --> 00:30:56,440
Isn't it sour?

330
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:00,800
It's sweet.

331
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:10,720
To be honest,

332
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,860
have you never liked me at all?

333
00:31:14,320 --> 00:31:16,320
Let's treat today as our first time,

334
00:31:17,280 --> 00:31:18,280
start over.

335
00:31:19,240 --> 00:31:20,570
Everything from before

336
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:21,960
doesn't count.

337
00:31:24,600 --> 00:31:26,080
I've never met anyone

338
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:28,480
who treats me the way you do.

339
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:31,440
If I let you go now

340
00:31:31,840 --> 00:31:33,900
because of what happened in the past,

341
00:31:34,760 --> 00:31:36,420
then I'd definitely be a fool.

342
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:57,840
Need help?

343
00:32:00,200 --> 00:32:00,960
What?

344
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:02,160
The water.

345
00:32:02,240 --> 00:32:04,440
I see you're having trouble opening it.

346
00:32:07,280 --> 00:32:08,610
Do you have a boyfriend?

347
00:32:39,320 --> 00:32:40,640
Your ordered meal.

348
00:32:40,800 --> 00:32:42,000
Are you following me?

349
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,440
I couldn't help falling

350
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:44,240
Why?

351
00:32:44,360 --> 00:32:45,620
for you at first sight.

352
00:32:49,360 --> 00:32:50,240
Are you cold?

353
00:32:50,600 --> 00:32:52,330
I won't be cold if you come down.

354
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:53,440
I love you.

355
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:55,920
I need time to adjust.

356
00:32:56,360 --> 00:32:57,800
How long will that take?

357
00:32:57,920 --> 00:32:59,720
The Earth revolves around the sun.

358
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:00,520
Revolution is too long,

359
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:01,450
let's talk about

360
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,010
rotations instead.

361
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:04,440
Thirty rotations.

362
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:05,500
How about just one?

363
00:33:18,320 --> 00:33:20,600
When did you start liking me?

364
00:33:20,600 --> 00:33:21,800
The first time we met.

365
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:22,800
Why?

366
00:33:23,320 --> 00:33:25,450
We were destined from a previous life,

367
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:27,540
like meeting an old friend again.

368
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:31,810
I don't care that you led me before,

369
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:33,400
now I'll lead you.

370
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:10,199
Would you like some cake?

371
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:14,370
Let's eat together.

372
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:17,560
I'll cut it.

373
00:34:49,679 --> 00:34:50,760
Was my former self

374
00:34:51,520 --> 00:34:52,920
exhausting to you?

375
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:55,080
Be honest.

376
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:04,000
A little bit.

377
00:35:07,560 --> 00:35:09,160
What about these three days?

378
00:35:14,960 --> 00:35:15,820
Very relaxing.

379
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,120
Really good.

380
00:35:22,680 --> 00:35:23,960
I'm a liar,

381
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:26,460
but I had no choice.

382
00:35:28,200 --> 00:35:28,960
Alright,

383
00:35:29,560 --> 00:35:31,720
let's not talk about this anymore.

384
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:35,680
When we were looking for Zhou Tong together,

385
00:35:35,680 --> 00:35:36,960
Wen Xiaoyao showed up,

386
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:39,600
and I started to worry about her,

387
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:42,920
so I pretended to forget the past

388
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:44,780
and called her to come to Beijing.

389
00:35:46,160 --> 00:35:48,480
I wish I could forget myself.

390
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,560
Forget yourself?

391
00:35:54,120 --> 00:35:55,720
Would you still know me then?

392
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:58,720
I'd want to.

393
00:36:00,240 --> 00:36:01,160
No matter what,

394
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,040
I'll always know you,

395
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,600
so stop overthinking.

396
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:17,810
Is the cake good?

397
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:19,890
It's delicious.

398
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:22,380
It doesn't matter,

399
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:25,420
whether it's the old Diandian

400
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:27,000
or the current Diandian,

401
00:36:28,000 --> 00:36:29,400
I like them both the same.

402
00:36:36,040 --> 00:36:36,970
Happy birthday.

403
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:52,500
The ballet company is rehearsing a new show.

404
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:55,320
Xiaoyao and Xiaomi are both starring in it.

405
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:57,960
They dance beautifully.

406
00:38:01,640 --> 00:38:03,170
Xiaoyao should be fine now.

407
00:38:03,640 --> 00:38:04,640
She's very strong

408
00:38:05,640 --> 00:38:06,770
and misses you a lot.

409
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:14,520
Mrs. Song is with Mr. Qiao now.

410
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:17,440
They'll be fine,

411
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,740
so don't worry about them.

412
00:38:22,280 --> 00:38:24,600
The girl who took you to the hospital after the accident

413
00:38:24,600 --> 00:38:25,860
is named Shi Diandian.

414
00:38:26,680 --> 00:38:28,080
She's my wife now.

415
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:34,940
We've been living in Beijing for a while now,

416
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:38,080
and we've discovered that real life

417
00:38:38,320 --> 00:38:39,520
and genuine love

418
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:41,700
can heal the wounds in our hearts.

419
00:38:43,560 --> 00:38:45,890
The two of us, who grew up without mothers,

420
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:48,040
can now comfort each other.

421
00:38:50,520 --> 00:38:52,050
We're going to be just fine.

422
00:39:22,520 --> 00:39:23,720
Zhao Gang (Aunt Gang)

423
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:24,840
Xiao Ru

424
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:59,490
Lighting Assistant

425
00:40:07,640 --> 00:40:08,300
Set Manager

426
